<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>


<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Profile</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/weather.png">
</head>

<body>
    <div>
        {{>header}}
        <!-- Projects start-->
        <section id="projects">

            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="text-center text-capitalize pt-5">NodeJs Projects</h1>
                <hr class="w-25 mx-auto pt-5">

                <div class="row text-center mb-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="display-4">Weather app</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="text-justify">This nodeJs app fetches live weather information for the location
                            provided by the user.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-justify"> Tech stack: ExpressJs, NodeJs, Vanilla Js</p>

                        <a href="https://tushar-node-weather-website.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2">Check it out</a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/tusharubale20/node-weather-website" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2 ">
                            <div class="fa fa-github"></div>&nbsp;Git link
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <hr class="w-50 mx-auto pt-5">

                <div class="row text-center mb-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="display-4">COVID-19 tracker app</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="text-justify">This nodeJs app fetches live COVID-19 data and
                            uses it to displays the COVID-19 data for each country.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"> Tech stack: ExpressJs, NodeJs, Vanilla Js</p>

                        <a href="https://tushar-covidapp.herokuapp.com/covidapp" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2">Check it out</a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/tusharubale20/covidapp" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2">
                            <div class="fa fa-github"></div>&nbsp;Git link
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <hr class="w-50 mx-auto pt-5">
                <div class="row text-center mb-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="display-4">Task manager app</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="text-justify">This is a complete backend app where users
                            can create tasks. As of now, it can be done through various API endpoints
                            for user creation, login,logoff, user info modify, task creation, task delete, task modify,
                            user avatar upload, etc. Frontend is yet to be created.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-justify"> Tech stack: NodeJs, ExpressJs, MongoDB, Mongo Atlas, Mongo Compass,
                            Jest
                        </p>
                        <span class="d-inline-block" tabindex="0" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="right"
                            title="Button is disabled as i am yet to create the frontend for it.">
                            <a href="#" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2 disabled">Check it out</a>
                        </span>
                        <a href="https://github.com/tusharubale20/task-manager-api" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2">
                            <div class="fa fa-github"></div>&nbsp;Git link
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <hr class="w-50 mx-auto pt-5">

                <div class="row text-center mb-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="display-4">Chat application</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12 py-2">
                        <p class="text-justify">Attempt at creating a chat room application where
                            a user can join in the room and chat with others in that room.
                            To simulate multiple users for chat room, you can hit the live project link
                            from two different tabs of the browser and login with different username and same
                            room name.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-justify"> Tech stack: ExpressJs, NodeJs, Vanilla Js,Websocket protocol, Socket.io
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://tushar-converse.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2">Check it out</a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/tusharubale20/chat-app" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-primary mx-3 my-2">
                            <div class="fa fa-github"></div>&nbsp;Git link
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <hr class="w-50 mx-auto pt-5">

            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Projects end-->


        <!-- JS, Popper.js, and jQuery -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </div>

    {{>footer}}

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>

</html>